
Ranger Help for: fetch
======================

SYNTAX:      fetch <what> from <whom>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE EXP:    NA
BASE SP:     variable

SUMMARY:    
This task allows a follower to fetch an item off of the ground in the
same room of any player that is in the same domain. Communicate with
the player you are having your fetch from to have the item on the
ground and use the correct syntax. If the player is where the follower
can reach them, the item will be fetched. This is a medium task so
only fairly smart followers can learn it.

